Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
write_lec_dft_constraints(25.10)              write_lec_dft_constraints(25.10)

Name
       write_lec_dft_constraints

Syntax
        write_lec_dft_constraints <dictionary>

       Type: String

       Default: ""

       This  variable  is  a  TCL  dictionary  that holds the LEC DFT pin con-
       straints from the last LEC run by Genus. It is passed  forward  through
       the  write_design  command. The write_do_lec command will automatically
       include this constraint in the do file.

Related Information
              * write_do_lec

